BOOKING.COM PRICE DROP ALERT
============================

Hi <%= @user.email %>,

Great news! The following hotel prices have dropped:

<% @price_drops.each do |drop| %>
<% currency_symbol = drop[:currency] == "USD" ? "$" : "€" %>
<%= drop[:hotel_name] %> (<%= drop[:city_name] %>)
<% if drop[:room_name].present? %>Room: <%= drop[:room_name] %>
<% end %>Dates: <%= drop[:check_in].strftime("%d %b") %> - <%= drop[:check_out].strftime("%d %b %Y") %>
